<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="faithfully-adv">faithfully <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'feɪθfəli/    美 /'feɪθfəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>忠诚地；忠实地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He had served the family faithfully for forty years. 
他已经为这一家人忠心耿耿地服务了40年。</p></div></div>